      <p>Check-in inspections are free for individual accounts. No credits are consumed for check-in inspections.</p>
      <h3>Failed payments</h3>
      <p>If a subscription payment fails, access to paid features will be suspended until payment is resolved. Your data will be retained for 90 days after suspension.</p>
